  <brief_title>A Trial of Pyridoxamine to Lower Urine Oxalate in Subjects With Stone Disease or Hyperoxaluria</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Pyridoxamine on Oxalate Excretion in Stone Disease and Hyperoxaluria</official_title>
