  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine whether pyridoxamine can decrease oxalate excretion in subjects who have normal
      oxalate excretion (but who have had kidney stones), and in subjects who have primary
      hyperoxaluria.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
